properties.documentation: Populates the following links and satellites:

Create five new Travel Money Card account based measures:
  • Foreign Exchange Transactions Reload AUD ($)
  • Foreign Exchange Transactions Purchase AUD ($)
  • Foreign Exchange Transactions Reload AUD (No)
  • Foreign Exchange Transactions Purchase AUD (No)
  • Quality New Account (No)
Four new shadow specific department dimensions (Attribution Department, Initiation Department, Funding Department and Approval Department) introduced in SMS bridge table.

• Create new co-existence view P_V_COX_001_STD_0.YCS_EVNT_DETL. It's required for measure derivation.
  • Populate Account Product and Account Portfolio links and satellites for YCS accounts
